## Iana.LanguageTagExtensions.JarConverters.loadRawLanguageTagExtensionsRegistryFromString() function

Parses a text (JAR) format language tag extensions registry from string content and returns the registry format with field names matching legacy test JSON format ("Contact\_Email", "Mailing\_List").

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare function loadRawLanguageTagExtensionsRegistryFromString(content: string): Result<Model.LanguageTagExtensionRegistryFile>;
```
